Later in the 1480s DR,{{ToD-time}} Nymmestra joined the coalition to stop the [[Cult of the Dragon]] from summoning [[Tiamat]] to the [[Prime Material Plane|Material Plane]]. She and two other adventurers, [[Alaeros Margaster]] and [[Barrowin Undurr]],{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 2}} traveled from [[Neverwinter]] to [[Icewind Dale]] to fight stop the Cult from acquiring more power for their Dragon Queen. There, they joined forces with [[Halander Hardingdale]] and [[Talon Everhale]].{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 1}} Their adventures took them to the [[Flame Fault]] on [[Tuern]],{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 3}}{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 4}} to the city of [[Waterdeep]],{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 7}} and finally to the [[Well of Dragons]] in the [[Backlands]] of the west.{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 9}}

